<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Ms. Lor - College Counselor</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #eef3ff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #5b6cff;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        main {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #5b6cff;
        }

        p, ul {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Ms. Lor</h1>
    <p>College Counselor</p>
</header>

<main>
    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
        Ms. Lor is an experienced college counselor who has worked with students for more than 8 years.
        She specializes in helping students find colleges that match their academic goals and personal interests.
    </p>

    <h2>How She Helps Students</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>College research and selection</li>
        <li>Application timelines and organization</li>
        <li>College essay brainstorming and editing</li>
        <li>Scholarship and financial aid guidance</li>
        <li>Academic planning</li>
    </ul>

    <p><em>"Every student has a unique path, and my job is to help them find it."</em></p>
</main>

</body>
</html>